%N A131047 Triangle read by rows: (1/2) * (A007318 - A007318^(-1)) as infinite lower triangular matrices.
%C A131047 Let P = Pascal's triangle, A007318. Then form (1/2) * (P - 1/P). Exclude the initial row of zeros. The resulting triangle T(n,k) is for n >= 1, 0 <= k < n.
