%C A131047 A generalized set of analogous triangles: (1/(Q+1)) * (P^Q - 1/P), Q an integer, generates triangles with row sums = powers of (Q+1). Cf. A131048, A131049, A131050 for triangles having Q = 2,3 and 4, respectively.
